description:
Are you anxious and worried because of things you’ve experienced? Do you find yourself dwelling on negative things that happened in the past? Dwelling on negative events of the past can affect you emotionally, mentally, and even physically. What does the Bible teach about how to let go of the past? God doesn’t want you to strengthen the power of past negative experiences by dwelling on them today. Learn how to be free from the negativity of your past. Discover the peace of “forgetting what is behind.”
